item.title: Prayer bpn4903 in Vanuatu
item.description: ##PREA IA I BLONG TALEMAOT EVRI DEI, LONG MONING, LONG MEDEL DEI MO LONG NAET *Hu we i wantem talem prea ia i mas wasem tufala han blong hem, mo taem hem i stap was, hem i talem: Mekem han blong mi i kam moa strong, O God blong mi, blong hem i save holem Buk blong Yu long wan strong fasin we ol armi blong wol i no save winim hem.
